metadata.description:
'Doesn't Matter' was written because although you might think it doesn't matter, you never know the impact until you do it. 

I wanted to experiment with different production styles and see what I could create. Sat in the studio with an idea and inspiration, this is the result. 

There is something in this track that feels calming to me and is good for the soul. I hope you enjoy it as much as I did creating it. 

Vocal Credit to: Citizen DJ Project, Joe Smith Collection at the Library of Congress, Motion Picture, Broadcasting and Recorded Sound Division. 

Artwork by Ross.Cracked
Mastering by Rob Small Mastering
